@node introduction
                                                                 .

                                                                 :
                                                                 :
             __________________.______.      ________            :
          ._(___)_.   ___     _|      l_____\\_     /____________:_ _
          |       |----/      \        /     \   __/\      __    :
          l_______|   /_______/        |-----/_______\____       :
                              l________|(rLf)            /-------:-
                                                                 :
                                                                 :
                                                                 :
                                                                 .


Bulls v1.5 is a handy utility to show different bulletin-textfiles to the
AmiExpress server. However, it does differ from other bulletin-viewers in
several ways. More features included, and full support of the MCI-interface has
been implanted to try to make this door the best around.


The main reason why I coded this door is that most of the other doors I've tried
out have had a aweful design, bad cursor reading, poor display-routines and some
very-very (Sysop) unfriendly configuration possibilities.


Since I didn't like the ones I got hold of from others, I started to code
something for my own sake. - And this is it! :)


I'm currently working on Bulls v2.o which I hope will be even better than this
version. I coded this before I started on the Zippy-Search, so... Much can be
improved in future releases, and all registered users WILL notice the benefit
of it! :)


           - - - --- ------[ lizard of megastyle! ]------ --- - -  -

@endnode






